snippet.title: Perennial Order | Official 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist & Play the Demo on Steam | https://t.co/yLksRBJc2L

Perennial Order is a dark, atmospheric Boss Rush game with horror elements and Co-Op in a 2D painterly style. Coming 2024.
